<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.UFI_PTASKmailUtil</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>UFI_PTASKmailUtil</name><script><![CDATA[var UFI_PTASKmailUtil = Class.create();
UFI_PTASKmailUtil.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
	
getUserIDfromEmailTo : function(emailTo){
		
		var string = emailTo;
var array = new Array();
array = string.split(",");

for (var i=0; i<array.length ; i++){
  

		var filterUserID = new GlideRecord('sys_user_group');
	    filterUserID.addQuery('u_multiple_emails_for_this_group', array[i]);
		filterUserID.query();
		while(filterUserID.next()){
			if(emailTo){
				return filterUserID.getValue('sys_id');
			}
			else{
				
				return gs.log('No assignment group found w.r.t the email received');
				
			}
		}
}	 
	},
    type: 'UFI_PTASKmailUtil'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>kush.bajpai</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-04-24 07:37:29</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>4d891ff0dbc1f34000a3f9971d96194e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>UFI_PTASKmailUtil</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_4d891ff0dbc1f34000a3f9971d96194e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>kush.bajpai</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-04-25 11:36:59</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
